      "content": "The migration will just terminate all active sessions and clear the cache. It won't \"handle\" them—it just wipes the instance to make room for the static models. The static models are designed for basic retrieval and simple queries, so for any high-level reasoning or complex processing, the client will just have to wait until the next hardware cycle or use a different provider. It's just the most efficient way to hit the energy goals right now.",
